          <fn id="btv101-TF2">
            <p>Because the coverage in this data set was low (100×) ViVan’s PPV was the lowest. However, ViVan demonstrated the highest sensitivity out of the three methods, identifying all but one of the variants found in the other. This datas<italic>et al</italic>so highlights the need for sequencing-error aware methods in order to reduce false positive calls such as the ones produced by naïve pileup.</p>
